data.description: Experience this immaculate and stunning single-story Lennar Radcliffe home, complete with owned solar panels, situated in the sought-after northwest Hanford community. This impeccable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a modern open floor plan centered around a large island, perfect for entertaining and family life. The luxurious master suite, complete with dual closets and a spa-like bathroom with a walk-in tiled shower, ensures a private retreat. With additional rooms tailored for a gym and home office, the flexibility and functionality of this home are unparalleled. Head outside to a dreamy backyard featuring a wood deck, an aluminum covered patio, and an inviting above-ground spa, all enhanced by the cost-saving benefits of owned solar panels. Just a short drive from NAS Lemoore, this home is not just a living space but a statement of lifestyle, combining elegance, comfort, and practicality in one stunning package.
